26
00:01:40,891 --> 00:01:42,960
Papa!

27
00:01:42,960 --> 00:01:45,002
Yes?

28
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:51,604
Papa!

29
00:01:51,604 --> 00:01:53,980
Yes, Jigsaw?

30
00:01:54,604 --> 00:01:56,205
Wow.

31
00:01:56,205 --> 00:01:57,820
