36
00:02:12,235 --> 00:02:15,335
Do you want to know what a cat looks like?

37
00:02:16,071 --> 00:02:18,071
Here it is.

38
00:02:18,071 --> 00:02:19,530
Puen!

39
00:02:19,530 --> 00:02:22,091
