51
00:02:51,486 --> 00:02:53,842
Come on, Jigsaw!

52
00:02:55,346 --> 00:02:57,081
I surrender!

53
00:02:57,081 --> 00:02:58,839
Puen!

54
00:02:58,839 --> 00:03:02,080
Do it, Jigsaw. Paint more!

55
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,403
Let go of me, Talay!

56
00:03:03,403 --> 00:03:05,022
More!

57
00:03:05,022 --> 00:03:07,422
- I surrender!
