78
00:04:55,272 --> 00:04:58,087
Puen! Where are you?

79
00:04:58,087 --> 00:05:00,160
I'm in the bathroom.

80
00:05:02,321 --> 00:05:05,584
Whoa. What a happy family.

81
00:05:05,584 --> 00:05:07,731
What happened to your faces?

82
00:05:08,292 --> 00:05:09,584
Ask your best friend here.

83
00:05:09,584 --> 00:05:11,440
Anyway, it's good you guys are here.

84
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:14,601
Can you help Jigsaw get dressed? He just got out of the shower.

85
00:05:14,601 --> 00:05:16,980
- Okay.
- Let's go, Jigsaw.

86
00:05:16,980 --> 00:05:19,027
Come on.

87
00:05:21,053 --> 00:05:23,704
- You can take a shower first.
- Wait.

88
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:27,311
