89
00:05:27,311 --> 00:05:29,099
Don't even try to get yourself out of this.

90
00:05:29,099 --> 00:05:31,810
My face is a mess because of you.

91
00:05:36,551 --> 00:05:37,960
Yes, sir.

92
00:05:37,960 --> 00:05:41,460
It's cute when Jigsaw pleads,

93
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:43,170
